toriality also provides the\nphysical meanings of some well-known mathematical results on fusion\n1-categories. This work can also be viewed as the first step towards a\nsystematic study of the category of local topological orders, and the\nboundary-bulk relation actually provides a useful tool for this study.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Feb 2015 19:42:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Oct 2015 13:07:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-23"}
